<DOCOLDNO>IA059-000323-B012-121</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/nationalreview/extra/010897x.html 204.71.237.92 19970114221302 text/html 2602
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 22:13:23 GMT
