<HEAD>
<TITLE>Events -- October Insider -- Heritage</TITLE>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<center><img src="/heritage/thf_log2.gif"><br>
<h3>Resource Bank</h3><p>
From the October Edition of <i>The Insider</i></center><br>
<center><h2>Events</h2></center><p>
<hr>

<P>
<B>Young America's Foundation Campus Speakers</B>
<P>
Upcoming events:
<P>
YAF sponsors conservative speakers to lecture on college campuses
across the country.
<P>
 October 22: Robert Novak at Syracuse University, Syracuse, NY
<P>
 October 22: William F. Buckley, Jr. at Stanford University,
Stanford, CA
<P>
 November 12: Robert Novak at the University of Chicago, Chicago,
IL
<P>
 November 13: Michael Medved at Williams College, Williamstown,
MA
<P>
CONTACT: Kristen Kingsley, 110 Elden Street, Herndon, VA 20170,
800/292-9231, fax 703/318-9122.<hr>
<P>
<B>Family Research Institute Seventh Annual Banquet</B>
<P>
