<h3>Resource Bank</h3><p>
From the September Edition of <i>The Insider</i></center><br>
<font size=5>New Heritage Publications</center></font><p> 

<P>
<B>Backgrounders </B>
<HR>
<P>
<ul>
<li> <a href="/heritage/library/categories/trade/bg1092.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">Restoring American Leadership in Latin America (No. 1092)</FONT></a>
<P>
<li> <a href="/heritage/library/categories/budgettax/bg1091.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">The Case for Repealing the Estate Tax (No. 1091)</FONT></a>
<P>
<li> <a href="/heritage/library/categories/budgettax/bg1090.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">How to Measure the Revenue Impact of Changes in Tax Rates (No. 1090)</FONT></a>
<P>
<li><a href="/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/bg1089b.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">Getting Backup: Twenty-One Steps Public Officials Can Take to Support Their Local Police (No. 1089)</FONT></a>
</ul><P>
<B>Backgrounder Updates</B>
<HR>
<P><ul>
<li> <a href="/heritage/library/categories/crimelaw/bgup279.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">The Clinton Administration's Continuing Retreat in the War on Drugs (No. 279)<BR>
</FONT></a>
</ul><P>
<B>Lectures</B>
<HR>
<P>
<ul>
<li> <a href="/heritage/library/categories/theory/lect571.html"><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Times New Roman">Is the Land of the Free Still the Home of the Brave?</a> by James Muller. (No. 571)</FONT>
<P>
