<center><h2>Events</h2></center>

<B>Young America's Foundation Campus Speakers</B>
<P>
<font size=3>Upcoming Events: February and March</FONT>


<P>
<B>Young America's Foundation Campus Speakers</B>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
6, 1996: P.J. O'Rourke at Washington &amp; Lee University (Lexington,
VA)</FONT>
<P>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
8, 1996: Dinesh D'Souza at Dickenson Law School (Carlisle, PA)</FONT>
<P>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
19, 1996: Dan Quayle at Northwestern University (Evanston, IL)</FONT>
<P>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
20 1996: Star Parker at University of South Florida-Tampa (Tampa,
FL)</FONT>
<P>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
21, 1996: Walter Williams at Weber State University (Ogden, Utah)</FONT>
<P>
<B><font size=3 face="monotype sorts"> </FONT></B><font size=3 FACE="Times New Roman">February
